==English==

===Noun===
'''jibber''' ([[jibbers]])

# A horse that [[jib]]s, i.e. refuses, stops short.
# {{nautical}}: {{substub}}
# {{rfv-sense}} Someone who backs out of plans at the last minute, thereby disappointing others.
# {{rfv-sense}} By extension, a person who never turns up when invited.
# {{rfv-sense}} Marijuana, used specifically to mean a rolled marijuana cigarette.

